reviewText: Geum, Na-Ra!  One of my all time favorite Korean characters.  The acting, ups & downs, and the writing are excellent.  A very funny and somewhat serious look at the Korean "moneylenders" and their trade. I never get tired of watching this drama and learn something new each time I watch.  As usual, the translation is somewhat rough, and it may be difficult for non-Korean speakers to follow, but you can still follow the story.  Park, Shin-Young always rocks!
